data.description: Welcome to 158 Richmond Road – a unique gem in the heart of a prime location! Unlike any other in the neighborhood, this home boasts proximity to Daphne, Foley, Gulf Shores shopping, and beautiful beaches, making it a rare find. Enjoy the tranquility of a quiet neighborhood with the added benefit of a great privacy backyard on a generous lot, complemented by a convenient garage at the front entry—no HOA fees to worry about! This property is a perfect opportunity, allowing you to customize and create your dream home.  The family room welcomes you with ceiling fan, wood flooring, vaulted ceilings, and a hallway to the breakfast/dining room with beautiful chandelier. Discover the charm of this 3-bedroom, 2.5 bathroom cottage in Popular Plantation Hills. The great room's vaulted ceiling adds character, and double doors lead you to the fenced backyard, and mature trees create a cozy atmosphere. Ideally situated near I-10, shops, restaurants, and the Eastern Shore Center, this home offers both convenience and comfort. This is it – your chance to own a piece of serenity in a fantastic location! Schedule your showing today and explore the potential nestled in the sought-after Plantation Hills subdivision, with access to the excellent Spanish Fort school district. Washer, dryer & refrigerator do not convey.
